<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000139/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """The assessment will include a control test that will take place after the laboratory sessions have been completed. It will account for 15% of the final grade, with a minimum required score of 3 out of 10.

At the end of the course, a project covering the topics addressed throughout the course will be evaluated. Intermediate reports will be handled to assess that the student is following the course successfully.

The extraordinary assessment will consist of a written exam and the submission of the project and the reports."""@es ;
